    ns1:associatedDate "1446-02-10"^^xsd:date ;
    ns1:biographicalOrHistoricalInformation "el. Colon. et Johannes [de Burgundia] olim Camerac. nunc el. Trever.: m. ad ep. Traiect. ut d. aepp. in possessionem bonorum eorum eccl. introducat vac. p. priv. Theoderici de Moersem olim aep. Colon. et Jacobi Sirik olim aep. Trever. et contra fautores d. rebellum procedat [= Baronius–Raynaldus 28, p. 459] 10. febr. 1446 V 378 26v–28r." ;
