<https://example.org/rg/lemma/10500466> a owl:NamedIndividual,
        ns2:Lemma ;
    ns1:preferredNameForTheSubjectHeading "Arnoldus Kael Arnoldus Kael Cael cler. Traiect. dioc., qui c. Theoderico Wayken pro alt. s. Crucis in par. eccl. in Cranenboch quod resign. p. Johannem Westvelinck de Clivis cler. Colon. dioc. procur. suum coram Johanne Lynepe prep. eccl. s. Gereonis Colon. perm. par. eccl. in Quaelburg Colon. dioc. 4 m. arg., de qua sibi primum auct. ordin. Theoderici [de Moers] aep. Colon. et deinde s.d. 27. decb. 30 prov. est" ;
    ns1:relatedPerson <https://example.org/rg/person/10501019>,
        <https://example.org/rg/person/10501020>,
        <https://example.org/rg/person/10510609>,
        <https://example.org/rg/person/10512406>,
